OL,7,FA date has been set for the inquest
OL,8,Finto the deaths of a mother and four
OL,9,Fof her children - almost seven years
OL,10,Fafter they died in a deadly arson
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FThe blaze claimed the lives of Demi
OL,14,FPearson, 15, her brother Brandon,
OL,15,Feight, and sisters Lacie, seven, and
OL,16,FLia, three.
