OL,7,FTheir mother Michelle Pearson suffered
OL,8,F68% burns to her body and "clung on to
OL,9,Flife" until she died, aged 37, on
OL,10,FAugust 25 2019 ` 20 months after the
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FShe had "begged" to be rehoused and
OL,14,Fcalled police on five occasions in the
OL,15,Ftwo weeks before the fatal attack, the
OL,16,Ftrial of her killers heard.
