OL,7,FZak Bolland and David Worrall were
OL,8,Fboth given four life sentences and
OL,9,Ftold they would serve a minimum of 40
OL,10,Fand 37 years respectively for the
OL,11,Fpetrol bomb attack on the Pearson
OL,12,Ffamily home on Jackson Street in
OL,13,FWalkden, Greater Manchester, in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of 11 December 2017.
OL,16,FBolland's girlfriend, Courtney
OL,17,FBrierley, 20, was jailed for 21 years
OL,18,Ffor four counts of manslaughter after
OL,19,Fthe trial at Manchester Crown Court in
OL,20,F2018.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
