OL,5,Cpublic
OL,7,FA major safeguarding review was
OL,8,Flaunched into how authorities,
OL,9,Fincluding the council, police and
OL,10,Fhealth officials, handled contact with
OL,11,Fthe family before the fatal attack.
OL,13,FBut at a pre-inquest review at Bolton
OL,14,FCoroners Court on Tuesday, the hearing
OL,15,Fwas told the report into the
OL,16,Fsafeguarding review was not to be made
OL,17,Fpublic.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
