OL,7,FSophie Cartwright KC, representing
OL,8,FSalford City Council children's
OL,9,Fservices, said a decision had been
OL,10,Fmade at a "national level" not to
OL,11,Fpublicise the report.
OL,13,FSenior coroner for Greater Manchester
OL,14,FWest Timothy Brennand said a copy of
OL,15,Fthe report was provided for his
OL,16,Finspection, which he said was
OL,17,F"revelatory of matters that I thought
OL,18,Fwere important".
