OL,7,FMr Brennand said the local authority
OL,8,Fwas not trying to be "obstinate", but
OL,9,Fpublication of the report could lead
OL,10,Fto "potential ramifications" for other
OL,11,Findividuals.
OL,13,FBut he added: "We are going to be
OL,14,Fcanvassing these matters in any event."
OL,16,FHe said an issue for the inquest will
OL,17,Fbe whether a real and immediate risk
OL,18,Fto the family ought to have been seen
OL,19,Fand whether "acts or omissions" by
OL,20,Fagencies had a "causative bearing on
OL,21,Fthe outcome."
