OL,7,FMrs Pearson's home was previously
OL,8,Fattacked, its windows and doors
OL,9,Fsmashed, graffiti sprayed on the walls
OL,10,Fand her wheelie bin set on fire, the
OL,11,Ftrial of her killers heard.
OL,13,FEach time police attended and she
OL,14,Fnamed Bolland as responsible.
