OL,7,FShe saw at least six different
OL,8,Fofficers, statements were made, risk
OL,9,Freferral forms completed, fire service
OL,10,Fpersonnel carried out two "safe and
OL,11,Fwell" visits, the family social worker
OL,12,Fwas informed and social services
OL,13,Falerted.
OL,15,FMrs Pearson told her housing provider,
OL,16,FCity West, she did not feel safe at
OL,17,Fhome with her children and wanted out.
OL,19,FCity West said it never received any
OL,20,Frequest for a move, believed to have
OL,21,Fbeen handled by Salford City Council.
