OL,7,FOfficers from Greater Manchester
OL,8,FPolice (GMP) took a statement from Mrs
OL,9,FPearson on the night of the fire,
OL,10,Fhaving been called out after Bolland
OL,11,Fhad been round "kicking off".
OL,13,FIt is not clear if officers
OL,14,Fimmediately actively sought out
OL,15,FBolland, who lived around 300 yards
OL,16,Ffrom her and was at home at the time
OL,17,Fthe officers called.
OL,19,FHours later he returned to the
OL,20,FPearsons' home armed with two petrol
OL,21,Fbombs.
